# Team Agent Standards Path

When working with shared team standards, reusable rules, long-form standards, or Cursor rule build outputs, prefer the local repository:

`/Users/lingqirui/team-agent-standards`

Use this path first for:

- `guidelines/*.md` agent-facing rules
- `docs/standards/*.md` human-readable standards
- `docs/skills/**/SKILL.md` reusable workflow skills
- `cursor-manifest.json` Cursor rule manifest entries
- generated Cursor rules under `generated/cursor/rules/`

Do not search broad filesystem locations before checking this repository. If the repository is missing or inaccessible, say so and ask for the updated path.
